  • What: Worksheet â HTML in 30 min
  • Result: Upload both verisons, more engagement
  • Key Insight: Options, not replacements

The process: 1. Took PDF of worksheet 2. Prompted AI: âConvert this to an interactive HTML exercise with instant feedbackâ 3. AI generated the code 4. Tested it quickly 5. Uploaded BOTH versions to Blackboard 6. Total time: Less than a coffee break
